        "### Vocabulary Builder\n",
        "\n",
        "Build a vocabulary from the **cleaned** corpus, keeping the **top 10,000 most frequent tokens**. \n",
        "All other tokens are mapped to `<UNK>`. We also add a `<PAD>` token for padding sequences."
      ]
